{"tid":2337123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衞生署倡手腕量體溫 醫生斥誤導","createTime":"2020-12-23T05:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T10:30:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbc377c07a73de1993a53c8e0b1ac228c0ebe01","tid":2337123,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:46:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/DL4HGLJPMBAMBLFLZGVXA67I5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FDL4HGLJPMBAMBLFLZGVXA67I5Q%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=3ca528bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FDL4HGLJPMBAMBLFLZGVXA67I5Q%2F&h=2ddf939d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/DL4HGLJPMBAMBLFLZGVXA67I5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生署倡手腕量體溫 醫生斥誤導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fMaNVFCqKpKl6TTl-Cws3aH_SNw=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WHXFVD4WCVGDTEDTCH7H2QPF2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfMaNVFCqKpKl6TTl-Cws3aH_SNw%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWHXFVD4WCVGDTEDTCH7H2QPF2A.jpg&h=b19a5d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■衞生防護中心提醒市民，手掌溫度易受天氣影響，應改以手腕等量體溫。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫境之下，市民已適應每到一個地方便要量體溫的習慣；但最近氣溫驟降，不少人用紅外線測量手掌溫度時，儀器均顯示「Lo」或33℃以下的超低體溫，有網民因此訕笑「冬天冇人發燒」。衞生防護中心昨在fb發帖「教路」，提醒手掌溫度容易受天氣影響，應改以手腕等被衣物覆蓋的部位量度皮膚表面體溫，讀數才較有參考價值。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：檢查染疫者喉嚨肺部  戴齊口罩面罩 西醫仍中招<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報實測 屢有偏差<br />\n<br />\n根據中心資料，由於手掌較常暴露空氣間，皮膚表面溫度較易被天氣影響，故不建議用手掌表面溫度作準。中心建議冬天應以手腕等部位代替手掌量體溫，因為手腕被衣物覆蓋，溫度較有參考價值。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者實測發現，用手掌量度，多次顯示「Lo」（體溫太低）或33℃以下讀數；手腕量度的體溫相對較高，曾讀得36.1℃的正常體溫，但有幾次顯示32.4℃的「超低體溫」。額探體溫讀數偏差最少，多次量得36℃及36.1℃。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：油塘紀律部隊宿舍淪疫廈<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">感染及傳染病科醫生曾祈殷認為中心的建議「簡直係匪夷所思」，「作為一個政府機構，點會建議咁樣量體溫？」他指額探是紅外線體溫計的正確用法，若手腕溫度較額探更具參考價值，「你有咩醫學文獻支持？」他擔心中心的建議會誤導公眾，提醒市民若懷疑發燒，應以耳探、口探等常規方法量體溫。</span><br />\n<br />\n手掌量體溫一直被指有欠準確，食衞局長陳肇始早前到葵涌石籬社區會堂臨時檢測中心視察時，曾用右手掌探三次熱均量不到體溫，結果改用左手再探才可入場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gktVWUIpbzvUv563qTgJxMSfgts=/661x1286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NPC35ZMXHFGF7G74VEXJWD6XTI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgktVWUIpbzvUv563qTgJxMSfgts%3D%2F661x1286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNPC35ZMXHFGF7G74VEXJWD6XTI.gif&h=2ba0a2ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03624bcaec06d01db8b6ff0349ec92aef41adf3e","tid":2337123,"uid":16676,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"油塘紀律部隊宿舍淪疫廈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93c3a52d351657e281464525f4d6c84d2ad2057","tid":2337123,"uid":9542,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"食衞局長陳肇始早前到葵涌石籬社區會堂臨時檢測中心視察時，曾用右手掌探三次熱均量不到體溫<br />\n<br />\n死人黎？"},{"pid":"84158b255b8a3d2cc8f425cbef657cf8d16b7f73","tid":2337123,"uid":305058,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"次次用隻手都係low<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔知邊個天才諗用手量體溫"},{"pid":"f8198d1cde50b79a2bc3ee023320372834cefe6f","tid":2337123,"uid":44882,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"84158b255b8a3d2cc8f425cbef657cf8d16b7f73","tid":2337123,"uid":305058,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:49:36.000Z","msg":"次次用隻手都係low<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔知邊個天才諗用手量體溫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"你可以隊個額頭埋去"},{"pid":"e9b73016e51fa7e2fea248862d97c3fc8d